<p><i>Blood Diamond</i> is the soundtrack to the movie of the same name. It was composed by <a href="/wiki/Academy_Award" title="Academy Award">Academy Award</a> nominated composer <a href="/wiki/James_Newton_Howard" title="James Newton Howard">James Newton Howard</a>, and won the 2008 Soundtrack of the Year Classical BRIT Award.</p>
