<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Blood_Diamond_(film)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Awards and nominations">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Awards and nominations</span></h2>
<p><b><a href="/wiki/79th_Academy_Awards" title="79th Academy Awards">79th Academy Awards</a></b></p>
<ul>
<li>Nominated for Best Actor In A Leading Role - <a href="/wiki/Leonardo_DiCaprio" title="Leonardo DiCaprio">Leonardo DiCaprio</a></li>
<li>Nominated for Best Actor In A Supporting Role - <a href="/wiki/Djimon_Hounsou" title="Djimon Hounsou">Djimon Hounsou</a></li>
<li>Nominated for Best Sound Mixing</li>
<li>Nominated for Best Sound Editing</li>
<li>Nominated for Best Film Editing - <a href="/wiki/Steven_Rosenblum" title="Steven Rosenblum">Steven Rosenblum</a></li>
</ul>
