<li><a href="/wiki/BFCA_Critics%27_Choice_Award_for_Best_Supporting_Actor" title="BFCA Critics' Choice Award for Best Supporting Actor" class="mw-redirect">Best Supporting Actor</a> - Djimon Hounsou</li>
