<p><a name="DVD" id="DVD"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Blood_Diamond_(film)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: DVD">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">DVD</span></h2>
<p>The <a href="/wiki/DVD" title="DVD">DVD</a> was released in Region 1 format on March 20, 2007. Both a single-disc and a two-disc version are available. High Definition versions on <a href="/wiki/HD_DVD" title="HD DVD">HD DVD</a> and <a href="/wiki/Blu-Ray" title="Blu-Ray" class="mw-redirect">Blu-Ray</a> have also been released. (Rating: R)</p>
